@@TJvBitBtn.HotTrack
Summary
  Specifies whether the button is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrack to true to provide visual feedback when the button is under the mouse. When HotTrack
  is false, there is no visual feedback when the mouse passes over the button.
See Also
  TJvExBitBtn.OnMouseEnter, TJvExBitBtn.OnMouseLeave

