@@TJvBitBtn.HintColor
Summary
  Determines the color of the Help Hint boxes of the button.
Description
  Use HintColor to specify the hint box color. Default this color has the value clInfoBk. To change
  the
  HintColor assign it a new TColor value.
See Also
  TJvBitBtn.HotTrack

