@@TJvBitBtn.DropDownMenu
Summary
  Identifies a pop-up menu associated with the button.
Description
  Assign a value to DropDownMenu to make a menu appear when the button is pressed (To display the
  menu programmatically, call the button’s Click method). If the menu’s AutoPopup property is set to
  true, the menu appears automatically. If AutoPopup is false, display the menu by calling the menu’s
  Popup method in the button’s OnClick event handler.

